{"type":"article","id":6199,"title":"蔡徐坤方面发表声明解除与NBA 合作关系","uid":3685,"topics":[2909,2922,2923,1384],"contents":"【蔡徐坤停止与NBA合作】蔡徐坤工作室8日发布声明，称蔡徐坤及其工作室坚决捍卫一个中国原则，坚决拥护祖国统一，坚决维护国家主权及领土完整，坚决反对任何企图分裂国家的言论和行为，从即日起停止与NBA的所有合作。今年春节，蔡徐坤曾作为NBA新春贺岁形象大使。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EGWOZIjUwAAWTsy?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EGWOZIjUwAAWTsy?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EGWOZIjUwAAWTsy?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-10-08","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}